          .title
            h2 Hello there, Stranger!
            span.byline Interested? Read on...
          p
            img.image.image-full(src='images/570_screenshots_2014-01-02_00001.jpg', alt='')
            | Source: 
            a(href='http://steamcommunity.com/app/570/screenshots/', rel='nofollow') Steam Workshop
          p
            | First off, what's Dota2? Dota2 is a pretty serious MOBA (for lack of a better word) which is also growing as an ESport. There's a sort of world championship every year called the 
            a(href='http://www.dota2.com/international/home/overview/', rel='nofollow') International
            |  held in Seattle, WA, US. The game is a 5-a-side tower defense game where you control a hero and accumulate levels by killing enemy heroes and creeps.
            | For more information, please visit the links at the bottom of the page.
          p
            | There are many strategies and combinations possible; a lot of traction is coming up with collecting stats. Dota2Stats can be used to analyse Dota2 game stats whichever way you want. You can write queries, and then visualize them using charts. 
            strong And if you like it, publish it for others to see!
